    if len(local_part) < 1 or len(domain_name) < 1:
        return ''
    domain_parts = domain_name.split('.')
    if len(domain_parts) < 2 or len(domain_parts[0]) < 1 or len(domain_parts[--1]) < 1:
        return ''
    return domain_name
